                <mxCell id="19" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 6px;&quot;&gt;create (&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(189, 10, 10);&quot;&gt;proxy&lt;/span&gt;): or gateway to work as translator between the client version and server, &lt;br class=&quot;soft-break&quot;&gt;- If the proxy/gateway supports a newer version than the request, it may upgrade the request&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 6px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&amp;amp; the proxy should send the response back in the same version the client used&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" parent="30" vertex="1">
